comment:
* Exception that may be supplied to the callback provided in {@link #requestModemActivityInfo}.
     * @hide

variables.name: ERROR_UNKNOWN
variables.comment: Indicates that an unknown error occurred

variables.name: ERROR_PHONE_NOT_AVAILABLE
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the modem or phone processes are not available (such as when the device
         * is in airplane mode).

variables.name: ERROR_INVALID_INFO_RECEIVED
variables.comment: * Indicates that the modem supplied an invalid instance of {@link ModemActivityInfo}

variables.name: ERROR_MODEM_RESPONSE_ERROR
variables.comment:
* Indicates that the modem encountered an internal failure when processing the request
         * for activity info.
